longBusinessSummary: Hapbee Technologies, Inc., a wellness technology company, provides nonionizing, non-thermal, and non-invasive wearable product under the Hapbee name. The company was formerly known as Elevation Technologies, Inc. and changed its name to Hapbee Technologies, Inc. in May 2020. Hapbee Technologies, Inc. was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
